These tests are to be undertaken following a successful install of Xubuntu.

Network connections
Ensure you have access to several methods to connect to Internet (1)
<dl>
    <dt>connect to them all (1)</dt>
        <dd>You are able to connect as expected</dd>
</dl>
[False Condition] 
<dl>
</dl>


If you have other partitions...
<dl>
    <dt>Open Thunar</dt>
        <dd>Confirm they are listed in <b>Thunar</b></dd>
        
	<dt>Confirm you are able to read files from it</dt>
		<dd>[FILL VERIFICATION]</dd>
