If you have USB drive available
Ensure you have a USB drive (2)
<dl>
    <dt>plug it in (2)</dt>
        <dd>The USB drive is mounted, Thunar opens and you can open files from USB</dd>
</dl>
[False Condition] 
<dl>
</dl>


